4556">Patrick England</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139688885164480"><h3 class="no_margin">Mats A. A. Persson</h3><p>  <sup>5</sup>  Karolinska University Hospital, Department of Medicine, Center for Molecular Medicine, Stockholm, Sweden,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Persson%20MA%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20174556">Mats A. A. Persson</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139688885162112"><h3 class="no_margin">Annette Martin</h3><p>  <sup>3</sup>  Institut Pasteur, CNRS URA3015, Unit&#x000e9; de G&#x000e9;n&#x000e9;tique Mol&#x000e9;culaire des Virus &#x000e0; ARN, Paris, France,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Martin%20A%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20174556">Annette Martin</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm139688884729664"><h3 class="no_margin">F&#x000e9;lix A. Rey</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup>  Institut Pasteur, CNRS URA3015, Unit&#x000e9; de Virologie Structurale, Paris, France,   </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Rey%20FA%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=20174556">F&#x000e9;lix A. Rey</a></div></div></div></div><div class="contrib-group half_rhythm fm-editor">Charles M. Rice, <span class="fm-role">Editor</span><sup></sup></div><div class="fm-panel half_rhythm"><div class="togglers"><a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm139688886020688_ai idm139688922892784_ai idm139688882143984_ai">Author information</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm139688886020688_an">Article notes</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm139688886020688_cpl">Copyright and License information</a> <a href="/pmc/about/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a></div><div class="fm-authors-info fm-panel hide half_rhythm" id="idm139688886020688_ai" style="display:none"><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff1">  <sup>1</sup>  Institut Pasteur, CNRS URA3015, Unit&#x000e9; de Virologie Structurale, Paris, France,   </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff2">  <sup>2</sup>  Institut Pasteur, Plate-forme d\'Analyse et de